        "description_en": "Discover a handwritten note inside a second-hand book and learn about a bookshop's hidden tradition.",
        "description_da": "Opdag en håndskrevet seddel i en brugt bog og lær om en boghandels skjulte tradition.",
        "description_it": "Scoprire un biglietto scritto a mano in un libro usato e conoscere una tradizione segreta della libreria.",
        "format": "dialogue",
        "speakers": json.dumps(["Customer", "Owner"]),
        "setup_type": "Discovery/Unexpected",
        "setup_summary": "A customer discovers a handwritten note inside a second-hand book and the bookshop owner shares the story behind the shop's tradition of hidden messages.",
        "body": (
            "Customer: Excuse me, I bought this book yesterday and I found something inside.\n"
            "Owner: Oh? What did you find?\n"
            "Customer: A handwritten note. It says, To whoever reads this next: I hope this story finds you at the right time.\n"
            "Owner: That's lovely. May I see it?\n"
            "Customer: Of course. Is this something that happens often?\n"
            "Owner: Actually, yes. We have a tradition here. Some customers leave notes inside the books they've loved.\n"
            "Customer: Really? How did that start?\n"
